title: Teemo Icon
body: I won a game of doom bots of doom but still haven't received my teemoing icon anybody else?

replies.body: *Ironfield* is right on the money, we're sending the icons out in batches and will continue doing so until the 17th. If you don't have it by then, reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll assist you further.
Hi fellow summoner, i believe riot is sending the icons  out until November 17th. If you don't have it by then, you can submit a support ticket and they'll help you out.
